      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/5b67b4ec-0bff-11e4-9892-5254006e85c2).  Ran 23 tests.  2 tests failed: sanity-sec, sanity.",
