    {
      "id": "f9dea0fe7b7dc6ea4818e35d0c739831664b1902",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 177,
        "name": "John Hammond",
        "email": "jhammond@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "jhammond"
      },
      "date": "2014-07-16 13:56:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nWhy revalidate for all opens?\n\nCan you explain more about why this is important? This will really slow down repetitive small file workloads and executables on lustre.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "c87973bf5d573b04870ec7f9279e61452e728ad0",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 112,
        "name": "Oleg Drokin",
        "email": "green@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "green"
      },
      "date": "2014-07-25 18:39:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThis will not slow down repetitive small opens or anything.\n\nYou see - all opens go to MDS anyway to get the open handle (if we don't have one cached, which we normally don't).\nSo the fact that we needed to do it from lookup vs from revalidate does not even register on the general scale of things.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "1eb414ef2f7f9b4bd76ee08ae1bd5fcdba578dff",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 112,
        "name": "Oleg Drokin",
        "email": "green@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "green"
      },
      "date": "2014-07-25 18:41:29.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review+2\n\nI should add, that when we confirm the revalidate, then the path we take in ll_file_open forces the server to issue an open lock which is frequently undesired because we amass a lot of them and it's kind of heavy to get rid of them (hence the lu4367 - slowdown during unlinks). Additionally we cannot properly use them from revlaidate anyway, as opposed to lookup, where we can do a single step lookup-open and return a file handle right away.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "9ae546ab199a1adf7c43ca5f7028bf695b1ba75c",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 112,
        "name": "Oleg Drokin",
        "email": "green@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "green"
      },
      "date": "2014-07-25 18:41:29.000000000",
      "message": "Change has been successfully cherry-picked as db5abf4b2b3fadc054a4e7d0d5a6b2fd9a99023c",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "5ebfee87ceafa3568ab341035db99f78672870f3",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 177,
        "name": "John Hammond",
        "email": "jhammond@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "jhammond"
      },
      "date": "2014-07-25 19:21:54.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nu:lustre-release# git describe\n2.6.50-54-ge8f8187\nu:lustre-release# cd /mnt/lustre\nu:lustre# cp /bin/true .\nu:lustre# time for ((i = 0; i < 10000; i++)); do ./true; done\n \nreal      0m30.220s\nuser      0m3.063s\nsys       0m25.740s\n \nu:lustre# cat /proc/fs/lustre/mdc/lustre-MDT0000-mdc-ffff8801dfb32b60/stats\nsnapshot_time             1406315982.466215 secs.usecs\nreq_waittime              32 samples [usec] 112 365920 382582 133922321102\nreq_active                32 samples [reqs] 1 2 34 38\nmds_getattr               1 samples [usec] 208 208 208 43264\nmds_close                 2 samples [usec] 331 456 787 317497\nmds_connect               3 samples [usec] 112 642 1222 643732\nmds_getstatus             1 samples [usec] 194 194 194 37636\nmds_statfs                2 samples [usec] 294 378 672 229320\nldlm_cancel               1 samples [usec] 419 419 419 175561\nobd_ping                  13 samples [usec] 229 446 4469 1588321\nseq_query                 1 samples [usec] 365920 365920 365920 133897446400\n \n...\n \nu:lustre-release# git describe\n2.6.50-55-gdb5abf4\nu:lustre-release# cd /mnt/lustre\nu:lustre# cp /bin/true .\nu:lustre# time for ((i = 0; i < 10000; i++)); do ./true; done\n \nreal      1m3.790s\nuser      0m4.828s\nsys       0m34.425s\n \nu:lustre-release# cat /proc/fs/lustre/mdc/lustre-MDT0000-mdc-ffff8801eaf453b8/stats\nsnapshot_time             1406315743.738274 secs.usecs\nreq_waittime              30035 samples [usec] 84 253260 10925285 68294966287\nreq_active                30035 samples [reqs] 1 2 30036 30038\nmds_getattr               1 samples [usec] 116 116 116 13456\nmds_close                 10001 samples [usec] 114 533 3151882 1047303170\nmds_connect               2 samples [usec] 110 623 733 400229\nmds_getstatus             1 samples [usec] 84 84 84 7056\nmds_statfs                2 samples [usec] 123 219 342 63090\nldlm_cancel               10000 samples [usec] 125 535 2911824 895480748\nobd_ping                  22 samples [usec] 174 456 6716 2187828\nseq_query                 1 samples [usec] 253260 253260 253260 64140627600",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
